                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190707-53-off282 t18190707-53-cd283"></join>, one shirt, value 10 s.; one coat, value 20 s.; one waistcoat, value 5 s., and ten neck-handkerchiefs, value 20 s.
